## 📋 Project Workflow

### 1️⃣ Data Loading

* Imported dataset
* Explored rows and columns
* Checked data types

### 2️⃣ Data Cleaning

* Removed duplicate records
* Handled missing values
* Fixed incorrect duration values
* Converted date columns to datetime format

### 3️⃣ Feature Engineering

Created new columns:

* Year Added
* Month Added
* Day Added

