## 📊 Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

Performed analysis on:

* Movies vs TV Shows
* Content Ratings
* Top Countries
* Top Directors
* Top Actors
* Movie Duration
* TV Show Seasons
* Release Year Distribution
* Monthly Content Addition
* Top Genres

---

## 💼 Business Questions Answered

✔ Which type of content dominates Netflix?

✔ Which countries produce the most Netflix content?

✔ Which year had the highest number of titles added?

✔ What are the most common content ratings?

✔ Who are the top directors on Netflix?

✔ Which genres are most popular?

✔ Which actors appear most frequently?

✔ What is the average movie duration?

✔ Which are the longest movies available?

✔ How many TV shows have 1, 2, 3... seasons?

---

## 📈 Key Insights

* 🎥 Movies significantly outnumber TV Shows on Netflix.
* 🌍 The United States contributes the largest amount of content.
* 🎭 Drama, International Movies, and Comedy are among the most common genres.
* ⭐ TV-MA is one of the most frequent content ratings.
* ⏱️ Most movies have a duration between **80 and 120 minutes**.
* 📺 Single-season TV Shows are the most common.
* 📅 Netflix rapidly expanded its content library during the late 2010s.

